stencil buffer works in online rendering and is hardware accelerated, but 
in offline rendering does not seem to work at all

FSAA works in online (with __GL_FSAA_MODE) but not in offline rendering

FSAA works now with 24bit color depth, but core dumps in 16bit (in call to 
glViewport)

AGPGART does not result in speed increase, but rather a decrease by 25%

AGP Driver seems to be reported wrongly as NVIDIA when going to NvAGP 0

texture mapping does seem to not work in offline rendering
